data.description: Make your boating dream a reality! This property offers a composite dock with 10,000lb boat lift with deep water access straight to Lemon Bay and the Gulf of Mexico AND NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED! Live your best Florida life and set sail to Manasota Beach, one of our pristine beaches, in a short 6-minute boat ride. The home has fabulous updates, including gorgeous luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout - even in the air conditioned 20x10 lanai that gives additional square footage. The kitchen offers refinished cabinets and stunning backsplash that enhances the beauty of the stainless-steel Frigidaire refrigerator, stove, and microwave (just purchased a year ago). The bathroom has a custom feature wall above the vanity and the shower has been completely redone, boasting breathtaking tile work, a luxury rain shower head and handheld shower wand, and frameless glass doors. The York air conditioner was just replaced June 12, 2020 and has a 10 yr. transferrable warranty. But that’s not all, the metal roof and hot water heater are new as of 2023 and the main sewer is lined as a preventative for any future issues.     The location is everything with only a 19-minute bike ride to the beach, the quaint and Historic Old Englewood Village just around the corner and conveniently located between the Punta Gorda and Bradenton airports. The association fees include lawn maintenance, pest control, replenishing of mulch twice a year, and maintenance of the community pool, shuffleboard and sea wall. *** Seller has paid phase I of the seawall replacement project in the amount of $8,400 and is providing concessions to cover the 2026 phase II estimated assessment in the amount of $11,500. *** It can't get better than this!
